Interface Stack<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - A generic placeholder representing the type of object to be stored in the stack.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LinkedStack

    public interface Stack<E>
    The Stack interface represents the public methods for the LinkedStack class.
